name: PHVideoRequestOptionsDeliveryMode
desc: Options for delivering requested video data, used by the deliveryMode property.

items.name: case automatic
items.desc: Photos automatically determines which quality of video data to provide based on the request and current conditions.

items.name: case highQualityFormat
items.desc: Photos provides only the highest quality video available.

items.name: case mediumQualityFormat
items.desc: Photos provides a video of moderate quality unless a higher quality version is locally cached.

items.name: case fastFormat
items.desc: Photos provides whatever quality of video can be most quickly loaded.
